Sharpe JAMES, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-202. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 513 Fed.Appx. 232 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
